node.text:
In honor of @thedoughnutproject turning 5 years old and Matty being really cute, here’s a throwback showing how the Mango Bango Doughnut started plus a history of Matty learning how to talk via doughnuts.
#👶🏽🍩 ❤️❤️❤️
#foodbabylovesthedoughnutproject
